#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, "
"floppy and &CD; drives, USB sticks &etc;) along with information on their "
"capacity, free space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and "
"unmount drives and view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; näitab saadaolevaid failiseadmeid (kõvaketta partitsioonid, "
"disketi- ja &CD;-seadmed, USB-pulgad &etc;) koos infoga nende mahu, vaba "
"ruumi, tüübi ja ühenduspunkti kohta. Samuti on võimalik seadmeid ühendada ja "
"lahutada ning neid failihalduris vaadata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; is similar to the &systemsettings; Storage Devices module, but "
"takes up less screen space. It is useful if you want to keep a &kdiskfree; "
"window available at all times."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; sarnaneb Süsteemi seadistuste salvestusseadmete mooduliga, kuid "
"võtab enda alla ekraanil vähem ruumi. See on päris kasulik omadus, kui "
"soovid &kdiskfree; akent kogu aeg kättesaadavana hoida."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "&kdiskfree; kasutamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "&kdiskfree; käivitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> at a command prompt or "
"select <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> from the <guisubmenu>System</"
"guisubmenu> group in the application launcher. The standard &Qt; and &kde; "
"command options are available, and can be listed by entering "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> at the "
"command prompt."
msgstr ""
"Anna käsureal korraldus <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> või "
"vali <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> rakenduste käivitaja alammenüüst "
"<guisubmenu>Süsteem</guisubmenu>. Kasutada saab &Qt; ja &kde; tavapäraseid "
"käsurea võtmeid, millest ülevaate saab käsuga <userinput><command>kdf</"
"command> <option>--help</option></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run the application as an applet in the systemtray, use "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Rakenduse käivitamiseks apletina süsteemisalves vali rakenduste käivitajas "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Süsteem</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The features of &kdiskfree; are also available in the &systemsettings; "
"module <guilabel>Storage Devices</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; omadusi saab kasutada ka Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis "
"<guilabel>Salvestusseadmed</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main window"
msgstr "Peaaken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &kdiskfree; window displays the available file devices."
msgstr "&kdiskfree; peaaken näitab saadaolevaid failiseadmeid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normally, the following pieces of information are included:"
msgstr "Tavapäraselt on näha järgmised infoväljad:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; peaaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kdiskfree; peaaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "an icon depicting the type of storage"
msgstr "ikoon, mis näitab andmekandja tüüpi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "device name"
msgstr "seadme nimi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "filesystem type"
msgstr "failisüsteemi tüüp"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "total size"
msgstr "kogumaht"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount point"
msgstr "ühenduspunkt"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "free disk space"
msgstr "vaba kettaruum"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "the percentage of space used as a number and as a graph."
msgstr "kasutatud ruumi protsent numbri ja graafikuna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on the header of a particular "
"column sorts the devices according to that variable. A second "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click sorts in the opposite order."
msgstr ""
"Klõps hiire <mousebutton>vasaku</mousebutton> nupuga mingi tulba päisel "
"sorteerib seadmed vastavalt selle tulba parameetrile. Teine klõps hiire "
"<mousebutton>vasaku</mousebutton> nupuga samal päisel muudab järjekorra "
"vastupidiseks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on a row pops up a menu. If that device is not "
"currently mounted, the <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> option is "
"available. If the device is mounted, it can be unmounted by choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem>. Selecting <guimenuitem>Open in "
"File Manager</guimenuitem> opens a new window with a graphical view of the "
"files on that device."
msgstr ""
"Klõps &HVNga; real avab hüpikmenüü. Kui seade ei ole parajasti ühendatud, on "
"aktiivne võimalus <guimenuitem>Ühenda seade</guimenuitem>. Kui seade on "
"ühendatud, on aktiivne <guimenuitem>Lahuta seade</guimenuitem>. Võimalus "
"<guimenuitem>Ava failihalduris</guimenuitem> seda teebki - avab uue akna "
"antud seadme failide graafilise vaatega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The setting for the file manager used by &kdiskfree; is independent from the "
"choice in the &systemsettings; module <guilabel>Default Applications</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; kasutatava failihalduri määramine ei sõltu sellest, mis on "
"valitud Süsteemi seadistuste moodulis <guilabel>Vaikimisi rakendused</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar and Configuration"
msgstr "Menüüriba ja seadistamine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Menüü Fail"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Update</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Värskenda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Immediately updates the display to reflect the current status"
msgstr "Uuendab kohe seadmete andmeid"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Fail</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Välju</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Closes</action> &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "<action>Sulgeb</action> &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Additionally &kdiskfree; has some common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information "
#| "read the sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui.html#menus-"
#| "settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
#| "html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgid ""
"Additionally &kdiskfree; has some common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks on &kdiskfree;l tavapärased &kde; <guimenu>seadistuste</guimenu> ja "
