"settings\">Menüü Seadistused</ulink> ja <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/ui."
"html#menus-help\">Menüü Abi</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Seadistustedialoog"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; seadistusteaken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kdiskfree; seadistusteaken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog has two tabbed windows, <guilabel>General Settings</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Mount Commands</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Sellel dialoogil on kaks kaarti: <guilabel>Üldised seadistused</guilabel> ja "
"<guilabel>Ühendamise käsud</guilabel>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Üldised seadistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the word <guilabel>visible</guilabel> or <guilabel>hidden</"
"guilabel> to turn display of an data field on or off."
msgstr ""
"Klõps sõnal <guilabel>nähtav</guilabel> või <guilabel>peidetud</guilabel> "
"muudab antud andmevälja nähtavaks või varjatuks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the update frequency by editing the value. The value in the box is "
"the interval (in seconds) between updates of the &kdiskfree; display to "
"reflect the current status."
msgstr ""
"Värskendamise sagedust saab muuta väärtust muutes. Kastis on näha intervall "
"(sekundites), mille järel &kdiskfree; värskendab andmeid seadmete kohta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>File Manager</guilabel> setting controls the command executed "
"when the <guimenuitem>Open Filemanager</guimenuitem> popup menu item is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Failihalduri</guilabel> sektsioonis saab määrata käsu, mis "
"käivitatakse, kui valida peaaknas kontekstimenüüst käsk <guimenuitem>Ava "
"failihalduris</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also two check boxes. One controls if a file manager window will "
"be automatically opened when a device is mounted. The other causes an alert "
"window to pop up if a disk gets critically full."
msgstr ""
"Seal on ka kaks märkekasti. Üks neist määrab, kas failihaldur avatakse "
"automaatselt seadme ühendamisel. Teine tekitab hoiatusakna, kui ketas täitub "
"kriitilise väärtuseni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Commands"
msgstr "Ühendamise käsud"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows the user to specify the mount and unmount commands for a given "
"device, as well as the icon used to represent it. More information on these "
"commands can be found on the man page for <application>mount</application> "
"(type <userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput> "
"at the command prompt)."
msgstr ""
"Võimaldavad määrata konkreetse seadme ühendamise ja lahutamise käsu ning "
"seadet tähistava ikooni. Rohkem infot nende käskude kohta leiab käsu "
"<application>mount</application> man-leheküljelt (anna käsureal korraldus "
"<userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput>)."

